### =======================================
### SkiNet API Tests (REST Client)
### =======================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ---------- Products ----------

### List all products (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### List products with small page size
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?pageSize=2

### List products sorted by price ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?sort=priceAsc

### List products sorted by price descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?sort=priceDesc

### Filter products by brand (e.g., brandId=1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?brandId=1

### Filter products by type (e.g., typeId=1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?typeId=1

### Search products by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?search=board

### Get single product by valid ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### Get single product by invalid ID (should 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/9999

### List all product brands
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/brands

### List all product types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/types

### ---------- Buggy / Error Simulation ----------

### Simulate 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/buggy/notfound

### Simulate 500 Server Error (null reference)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/buggy/servererror

### Simulate 400 Bad Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/buggy/bagrequest

### Buggy with valid ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/buggy/bagrequest/42

### ---------- Error Controller ----------

### Get 404 error response
GET {{baseUrl}}/errors/404

### Get 400 error response
GET {{baseUrl}}/errors/400

### Get 500 error response
GET {{baseUrl}}/errors/500
